{"page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Capgemini UK plc\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Data Centre Consolidation and Optimisation\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Capgemini manage data centres across the world for private and public sector clients. We understand that Data Centre consolidation is a key driver for reducing costs. This service will identify opportunities for optimisation and consolidation of data centres. Defining risk and illustrating transformation activities to help to reduce your TCO.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Define DC Capacity \u2013 What is your real current capacity?\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Cost Reduction Review\u2013 Analyse current cost base and identify opportunities\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Carbon Footprint Reduction \u2013 Investigate areas for carbon footprint reduction\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Resilience and Availability \u2013 Increase protection while optimising DC footprint\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Security Risk \u2013 Identify risks and profile mitigations\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Flexibility \u2013 Improve agility by building flexible solutions\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Optimization \u2013 Optimise workloads and align the service portfolio\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Rationalisation \u2013 Assess IT estate and identify decommission targets\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Consolidation \u2013 Target areas of duplication and reduce operational footprint\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Implementation \u2013 Define a transition strategy and migration plan.\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Reduce Operational Risk \u2013 Define, mitigate and remove Risks\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Reduce Data Centre footprint \u2013 Consolidate your data centre infrastructure\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Optimise workloads \u2013 Drive IT harder and improve ROI\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Consolidate IT portfolio \u2013 Reduce your service catalogue\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Economies of Scale \u2013 Identify syndicated service model opportunities\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Capacity for Growth \u2013 Transform workloads to improve utilisation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Define DC Strategy \u2013 planning for the future of DC\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Improve Resilience and Availability \u2013  services achieve right protection level\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Secure your Data \u2013 change without compromising security\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Promote Agility \u2013 Simplify portfolio of DC services\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3273 per person\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Month\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92224/6213085337485312-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92224/6213085337485312-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n     